data.description: Take a look and fall in love with this 2 story 4 bed/3.5 bath, 2-car garage beautiful home located in Oceanway in the Victoria Lakes community. This home is move in-ready! Major features includes a breathtaking chandelier entrance, an open floor plan with upgrades that includes crown molding, granite countertops, chandelier fixtures in the downstairs bathrooms, luxury vinyl flooring and tile in main areas downstairs and black appliances. Not to mention with a Huge Master Suite on the main level! Community splash pad and pavilion with pool. Easy access to I-295 & Dames Point. Near River City Marketplace, UF Health, and Jacksonville Zoo. New Hot Water Heater installed(2023), New Roof will be done by Closing date.
